com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval

Class ArrayTrainable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval.TrainableWrapper<DataTrainable>
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval.BatchedTrainable
        • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval.ArrayTrainable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataTrainable, Trainable, TrainableDataMask

    public class ArrayTrainable
extends BatchedTrainable
implements TrainableDataMask
    Basic training component which evaluates a static array of data on a network. Evaluation is subject to batch-size conditions to manage execution memory requirements.
